snippet.title: [Sky Ride] Official Trailer
snippet.description:
「Sky Ride」 3D action shooting game
Dodge enemy's attacks and shoot them down from all directions!
Devastate your enemy and compete other players on the online ranking!

PlayStation4.
For further informations, check out our homepage http://skyride.mutan.co.jp/ps4/en/
